nodes.text: Shaak Ti's Eta-2 Actis-class light interceptor
Togruta Jedi Master Shaak Ti owned an Eta-2 Actis-class light interceptor. At one point, she flew the interceptor over the oceans of the planet Kamino.

Shaak Ti's Eta-2 Actis-class light interceptor was first mentioned, along with an illustration, on a card in the Eta-2 Actis Expansion Pack, a 2020 expansion to the Star Wars: X-Wing Second Edition game.
